    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride at a great value? This car is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! While it shows some honest wear from its travels, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking a solid vehicle without the premium price tag. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a well-loved car that still has plenty of life left to give!",
